name: Barquin D'an
Lore: 'Bith musician and gambler. Estranged older brother of Figrin D''an. Plays kloo horn, but not as well as his brother. Briefly jammed with Max Rebo''s band.',
Text: 'Once during each of your control phases, may use 1 Force to make a ''wager.'' Both players draw two destiny (add 1 to your total destiny for each of your gamblers at same site). Player with highest total may retrieve 1 Force.',
